{"word":"H5930 - עֹלָה - ʻôlâh - o-law' - Ascent","slug":"H5930","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">עֹלָה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>ʻôlâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>o-law'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Ascent"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E2;&#x05D5;&#x05DC;&#x05D4;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05E2;&#x05DC;&#x05D4; - &#x201B;o&#x0302;la&#x0302;h  &#x201B;o&#x0302;la&#x0302;h</b> - <i>o-law', o-law'</i><p/>Feminine active participle of <a href=\"#/H5927\">H5927</a>; a <i>step</i> or (collectively <i>stairs</i>, as <i>ascending</i>); usually a <i>holocaust</i> (as <i>going up</i> in smoke): - ascent, burnt offering (sacrifice), go up to. See also <a href=\"#/H5766\">H5766</a>."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H131\">H131</a>, <a href=\"#/H4605\">H4605</a>, <a href=\"#/H4607\">H4607</a>, <a href=\"#/H4608\">H4608</a>, <a href=\"#/H4609\">H4609</a>, <a href=\"#/H4610\">H4610</a>, <a href=\"#/H5920\">H5920</a>, <a href=\"#/H5921\">H5921</a>, <a href=\"#/H5927\">H5927</a>, <a href=\"#/H5929\">H5929</a>, <a href=\"#/H5933\">H5933</a>, <a href=\"#/H5935\">H5935</a>, <a href=\"#/H5940\">H5940</a>, <a href=\"#/H5941\">H5941</a>, <a href=\"#/H5942\">H5942</a>, <a href=\"#/H5944\">H5944</a>, <a href=\"#/H5945\">H5945</a>, <a href=\"#/H8585\">H8585</a>"}]}